title: He's Michigan Goff. Whitmer's building an electrified fence around her house?
subtitle: The conservatives denounced the security improvement planned by the Governor after opposing the expensive border wall of United States President Donald Trump.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: (Michelian Goff) Gretchen Whitmer, who has already spoken against the United States border wall with Mexico, receives security updates at her official home that include an eight-foot electric fence.
